OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FAround 500 artworks by Bagpuss and
OL,8,FBasil Brush creator Peter Firmin are
OL,9,Fgoing up for auction in Kent after
OL,10,Fbeing uncovered in his home.
OL,12,FThe artist and puppet maker - who died
OL,13,Faged 89 in 2018 - co-created several
OL,14,Fpopular children's TV programmes,
OL,15,Fwhich also included The Saga Of Noggin
OL,16,FThe Nog, Ivor The Engine, The
OL,17,FClangers, and Pogles' Wood.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
