FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784720909
OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FHundreds of Firmin's original artworks
OL,8,Fhave been discovered at his home in
OL,9,FKent and will be auctioned on Friday
OL,10,FJuly 31 and Saturday August 1 in a
OL,11,Flive, online-only auction.
OL,13,FThe pieces include original
OL,14,Fwatercolours and pen drawings of his
OL,15,Ffamous characters, storyboards from
OL,16,Fbooks and TV shows and rare,
OL,17,Fcollectible toys and games - as well
OL,18,Fas Firmin's personal art, mainly
OL,19,Flinocuts and engravings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784720909
OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FThey were found while his family
OL,8,Ffarmhouse and outbuildings were being
OL,9,Fcleared for sale.
OL,11,FKaty Firmin, the fourth of Firmin's
OL,12,Fsix daughters, said: "My family have
OL,13,Flived here in Blean since 1959 and
OL,14,Fwhen opening various cupboards have
OL,15,Ffound things we simply didn't know
OL,16,Fexisted."
OL,18,FShe continued: "It's an emotional
OL,19,Fwrench.
OL,26,@tD@VOUxD@IO]zD@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784720909
OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,F"But there are just so many things, he
OL,8,Fnever threw anything away.
OL,10,F"The six of us have all kept things
OL,11,Fthat we particularly love but it's
OL,12,Ftime to share the rest.
OL,14,F"People have such fond memories of
OL,15,Fcharacters like Bagpuss and now they
OL,16,Fhave the chance to own a little bit of
OL,17,Ftheir childhood."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
