OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784720909
OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FThe auction is being held by The
OL,8,FCanterbury Auction Galleries, which
OL,9,Fhas called the items a "treasure
OL,10,Ftrove" and described it as the largest
OL,11,Fcollection of Firmin's work to ever
OL,12,Fcome up for auction.
OL,14,FIt said some of the highlights of the
OL,15,Fsale include Firmin's hand-painted
OL,16,Fillustrations, on which changes and
OL,17,Fcorrections he made along the way can
OL,18,Fbe seen.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784720909
OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FThere are also collectible models of
OL,8,Fmany characters from shows such as The
OL,9,FClangers and Bagpuss, and original
OL,10,Fillustrations from storyboards and
OL,11,Fbooks, including hand-drawn
OL,12,Funpublished book attempts discovered
OL,13,Fat the house.
OL,15,FCanterbury Auction Galleries
OL,16,Fspecialist valuer Susanna Woodgate
OL,17,Fsaid it is a "privilege to now be able
OL,18,Fto offer people a chance to own
OL,19,Foriginal pieces of his work".
OL,26,@yD@NOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
