OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784720909
OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,F"Cataloguing the items has been a real
OL,8,Fnostalgia trip," she added.
OL,10,FThe Firmin family are also now
OL,11,Fdonating the original Bagpuss and
OL,12,Foriginal family of The Clangers to
OL,13,FCanterbury's Beaney museum, where they
OL,14,Fhave been on loan.
OL,16,FFirmin - who received the Bafta
OL,17,Flifetime achievement award in 2014 -
OL,18,Fcreated Smallfilms with Oliver
OL,19,FPostgate, who died in 2008.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
