FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784720909
OL,3,C'Treasure trove' of 500 artworks by
OL,4,CBagpuss creator Peter Firmin up for
OL,5,Cauction
OL,7,FWhile Firmin made the puppets, sets
OL,8,Fand backdrops, Postgate wrote most of
OL,9,Fthe stories and narrated the TV shows.
OL,11,FTheir first hit was in 1959 with Ivor
OL,12,FThe Engine, about a Welsh steam
OL,13,Flocomotive who wanted to sing in a
OL,14,Fchoir.
OL,16,FThe first, hand-drawn comic strip of
OL,17,FIvor is included in the sale.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
